{"tid":2513781,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"曼聯球場示威　2名警員受傷  警方將會起訴涉事人","createTime":"2021-05-02T21:01:12.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-02T22:16:58.000Z","uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0798b7c9e9764798d3144283eaa341cbcf0a1f41","tid":2513781,"uid":227801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T21:01:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/international/2389856\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Finternational%2F2389856&d=LCDPOb8M8FyYKm9nuxOGtUYnXQRGGZgEWtwyrMN1cgk%3D&h=7abd328d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/international/2389856</a><br />\n英超聯首次有賽事因球迷示威而押後。曼聯數千名不滿美國班主格拉沙家族的球迷在紅魔鬼主場迎戰利物浦前，去到奧脫福球場外示威，約200人更衝入球場草坪。警方到場驅散，有2名警員在衝突中受傷。賽事被迫押後。<br />\n格拉沙家族在2005年以槓桿方式收購曼聯，令球會負債累累。曼聯早前聯同其他11支歐洲頂級球會，成立歐洲超級聯賽，最後在多方批評及反對下，與另外5支英超球會宣佈退出。到場示威的球迷施放煙霧，又高叫口號，要求格拉沙家族出售曼聯股權。曼聯發表聲明，指球迷對曼聯充滿熱情，球會完全認同他們和平示威及自由表達的權利，但對危及其他球迷、職員及警員的行動感到遺憾。警方說，其中一名受傷警員被玻璃樽掟中面部，需要送院救治，亦有曼聯職員一度要將自己反鎖在房間。警方正調查事件，將會起訴涉事的人。"},{"pid":"a98f548d5025a06c58ad117f88af39aef4068345","tid":2513781,"uid":227801,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T21:04:43.000Z","msg":"影曬大頭啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://ipfs.infura.io/ipfs/QmWJCdEFUhtoGdEsk5HFBBrsCfH8WGpYj78vxdBzZp4vYY?filename=2y26g4o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2y26g4o.jpg&h=538757a9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d782e82eb2fc281ec4fa419ee13316d0de13093a","tid":2513781,"uid":27664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a98f548d5025a06c58ad117f88af39aef4068345","tid":2513781,"uid":227801,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T21:04:43.000Z","msg":"影曬大頭啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2y26g4o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2y26g4o.jpg&h=538757a9&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T21:51:52.000Z","msg":"影相都要拉底口罩 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0f8e7ee4442e27a300676f6f905b40bd050aef5","tid":2513781,"uid":46587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T22:06:21.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b080c338a24e692d8cc9867751d2c182e76d6e94","tid":2513781,"uid":388403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a0f8e7ee4442e27a300676f6f905b40bd050aef5","tid":2513781,"uid":46587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T22:06:21.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T22:14:33.000Z","msg":"屌你老母"},{"pid":"e1a34cbe7017d6539d02cb17b34f320a80e67353","tid":2513781,"uid":308107,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T22:15:22.000Z","msg":"死黑警又殺人<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c57ca11c38f045e6244d30fb31fb6fb857d7d66","tid":2513781,"uid":99700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-02T22:16:58.000Z","msg":"612無錢幫喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}